{
  "stem": "22944.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, if you know the continental, they used to outside in a-- behind all the cottages, there was sort of a-- a hole in the ground.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was disinfected from time to time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember, that was the toilet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And washing was done in a barrel in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the laundry, my mother used to do outside in a-- in a yard.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "See, she was very, very busy lady, was doing what as much as she could do.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] I think that the neighbors started to call us names-- the neighbor flat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the children wouldn't play with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was quite a surprise, because we used to play in the street hopscotch and all those kids games-- skipping ropes.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember we used to jump around like all the children play.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They wouldn't-- call us names, started to throw stone at us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And decree started to come.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Jewish people have to wear the Star of David.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my father must have got the information, again, from the Jewish center, the synagogues that he used to attended every day.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And the scarce of food started to be.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we started very, very basic-- a lot of beans I remember eating at home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So obviously, that was a vegetable, because it was a farm area and not far.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In the town there were a lot of farmers, so we had quite a bit of vegetables still.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was still at school, but quite often was disrupted.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my feeling was, if my father used to come home and discuss it and things with my mother-- I got a memory that I never remember seeing my parents rowing.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
